lead_paragraph: Kyle Lowry scored 32 points, DeMar DeRozan added 31 and the Toronto Raptors beat the Utah Jazz 104-94 on Wednesday night for their club-record 11th straight home win.

headline.print_headline: Raptors Beat Jazz 104-94 for 11th Straight Home Win
